label.phrase: live performance photography has its own uniques set of challenges low light and fast moving subjects can challenge even the most sophisticated photographic tools one speed bump encountered was nikon's decision to reposition the manual control readout traditionally the read out was along the bottom of the image area however the manual read out on the d3 is now displayed vertically on the right side of the image area

clusterList.phrase: live performance photography has its own uniques set of challenges low light and fast moving subjects can challenge even the most sophisticated photographic tools one speed bump encountered was nikon's decision to reposition the manual control readout traditionally the read out was along the bottom of the image area however the manual read out on the d3 is now displayed vertically on the right side of the image area

the d3 images captured on 13 dec 07 weren't the most dynamic music photos i've taken to date i'm even willing to concede that the images themselves are perhaps less interesting than the lessons i've learned with this new photographic tool however it's only with a commitment to unpaid practice that i can confidentially integrate the nikon d3 into my professional photography
